0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gregoria Mariska Tunjung\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregoria_Mariska_Tunjung\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregoria_Mariska_Tunjung\"}, {\"begin\": 359, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999622943967, \"rank\": 3.3152311035942666e-08, \"text\": \"Indonesia\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesia_national_badminton_team\"}, {\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999718406802, \"rank\": 2.8159270450609617e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6967977310929064, \"rank\": 0.22096759384825937, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  He Bingjiao of China was spotted holding a Spanish pin when she received the women's singles badminton silver medal on the podium at the 2024 Summer Olympic Games in Paris on Monday.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 523, \"end\": 528, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5941198585583451, \"rank\": 0.5706522690550019, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9869185891127329, \"rank\": 0.01300183423019481, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999718406802, \"rank\": 2.8159270450609617e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This pin was given to me by Team Spain,\\\" He explained at the press conference.\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 771, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 726, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.7824290185066824, \"rank\": 0.2772343941617575, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My opponent in the semifinals, Carolina Marin, had to pull out of the match because of injury.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 804, \"end\": 818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolina_Mar\\u00edn\", \"score\": 0.9999990899400066, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carolina Marin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolina_Mar\\u00edn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carolina_Mar\\u00edn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel sympathetic because Marin is an outstanding athlete and opponent.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 940, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to take her spirit with me to the final.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wish her a quick recovery.\\\"\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC) posted the photo of He on the podium on its Instagram account and praised her act.\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1026, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1026, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1108, \"end\": 1117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.441977239130049e-19, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He Bingjiao held the Team Spain pin during her medal ceremony in support for Carolina Marin, who suffered a knee injury yesterday in the semifinals,\\\" the IOC wrote.\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1175, \"end\": 1180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.7824290185066824, \"rank\": 0.2772343941617575, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 1303, \"end\": 1306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4842722006891738e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wished He Bingjiao all the best in the final, because sportsmanship was above all else,\\\" Marin said in a statement on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the moment on the podium is one of the loveliest gestures anyone has ever made to me and I will always be incredibly grateful to her.\\\"\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marin won the first game 21-14 and led 10-5 in the second in the semifinals.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she landed awkwardly on her right knee after an overhead smash.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Though she tried to continue after strapping on a knee brace, she soon realized that she wasn't able to play on and had to withdraw.\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marin was shedding tears of both disappointment and pain when her coach arrived.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He headed over to check on her opponent as well when the crowd applauded the Spaniard.\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2028, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9687018777850298, \"rank\": 0.030127244873480785, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gold medalist An Se-young of South Korea had been haunted by knee injury and sent her wishes for Marin.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2072, \"end\": 2083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9835578745849307, \"rank\": 0.012565825344966893, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Marin is a great athlete and a legend,\\\" An said.\", \"from\": 2148, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have learnt a lot from her.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel so sad that she could not continue to play.\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to play her again on the court.\\\"\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": []}]}"